{"tid":1442242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"快簽 呼籲美軍派遣醫療船","createTime":"2019-08-11T01:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T08:55:25.000Z","uid":273719,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"425a2f757647f1264f8c60121ca2fdd303af1eab","tid":1442242,"uid":273719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:34:26.000Z","msg":"陳雲：香港因為共產黨的國家恐怖襲擊，已經爆發人道災難。我呼籲國際救援組織&mdash;&mdash;例如無國界醫生到香港設立保護戰爭傷患者私隱及阻止暴政攻擊力量進入的戰地醫療服務。美軍的醫療船也應該駛入香港設立這類服務。<br />\n各位可以用英文在美國總統及參議員的Twitter留言，說明香港的狀況，呼籲美軍派遣醫療船來香港停泊救援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster?fbclid=IwAR3ti7ZS4Q51fMFKWKGHzH7lU3Ok80gT3qjXG-FBF4_sjqVU2gOK2Eepmb4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ti7ZS4Q51fMFKWKGHzH7lU3Ok80gT3qjXG-FBF4_sjqVU2gOK2Eepmb4&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbUwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=97961567\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster?fbclid=IwAR3ti7ZS4Q51fMFKWKGHzH7lU3Ok80gT3qjXG-FBF4_sjqVU2gOK2Eepmb4</a>"},{"pid":"acec902dd2b895efaae6065c3a1422ff9cc3f212","tid":1442242,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:53:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"917967b0cc93c9741de0191d61cd02ccba207e5b","tid":1442242,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b788cc0b994962e4b0bdecd03549de8e1e947f","tid":1442242,"uid":273719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:02:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"502e58d11d555c125b1cac51626fbd69f3be5dd3","tid":1442242,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:04:33.000Z","msg":"Push